1
00:00:08,371 --> 00:00:10,713
All right, so I'm Jennifer Brandes-Hepler,

2
00:00:11,034 --> 00:00:13,456
and I wanted to talk about exposition here

3
00:00:13,556 --> 00:00:17,360
because, show of hands, how many of you woke up today thinking,

4
00:00:17,560 --> 00:00:20,422
oh boy, I want to write a giant block of exposition

5
00:00:20,743 --> 00:00:22,945
that players are going to button through and forget almost

6
00:00:23,005 --> 00:00:23,585
immediately?

7
00:00:23,605 --> 00:00:27,689
All right, and how many of you have had to spend a work day

8
00:00:27,749 --> 00:00:29,091
or two doing exactly that?

9
00:00:30,582 --> 00:00:31,623
That's kind of what I thought.

10
00:00:31,824 --> 00:00:34,808
So now I'm going to stand here for 25 minutes

11
00:00:34,888 --> 00:00:36,611
and lecture you on why you should never

12
00:00:36,651 --> 00:00:39,094
have someone stand there for 25 minutes and lecture you.

13
00:00:41,077 --> 00:00:43,619
So let me start with a little bit of who I am.

14
00:00:43,879 --> 00:00:46,962
I've been working in games since the late 90s.

15
